text: Ropicosybra multipunctata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Pic in 1927. It is known from Vietnam.BioLib.cz - Ropicosybra multipunctata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Apomecynini Category:Beetles described in 1927
